\begin_inset Formula $\hat{s}/L$
\end_inset

, to study its effect on the detachment forces.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Maximum adhesion is seen when the hinge is positioned at the centre of the
 array, i.e.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{s}/L=0.5$
\end_inset

